{"tid":2515162,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"移民最難係面對父母","createTime":"2021-05-03T18:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T02:21:32.000Z","uid":26080,"like":96,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"89c75a67ab29617d3bbb7bd5693373de020222f2","tid":2515162,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T18:41:18.000Z","msg":"我係加拿大owp果班，批左一星期。鎖港條例原因下，今日同兩老講想提早8月前走，而家已經搵緊工同睇緊租邊。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗講都知佢地好唔捨得我。我當然有做足功課睇點樣帶埋父母去，但佢哋表達過幾次唔想走，因為佢哋真係開始老。而我已經有答案，我好大機會係走。走咗仍然會keep 住FaceTime 搵佢地，每年都會返黎（如果香港冇封）。如果佢哋有啲咩病，我都會飛返黎照顧佢哋既，keep 住匯錢返黎俾佢地。<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有其他原因令我要走，但自爆野唔講，父母都唔知，因為一個藍，一個淺藍，而我把口又好密。佢哋只係以為我鐘意加拿大。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以分享下點處理兩老？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac0d592905af6a846692fec177f3d2e03b03e0a","tid":2515162,"uid":336524,"like":32,"dislike":8,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T18:43:02.000Z","msg":"走咪走<br />\n係咁架啦"},{"pid":"9a0f18ba972ca82667f59b560ac510e05d88ca05","tid":2515162,"uid":171800,"like":51,"dislike":2,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T18:51:20.000Z","msg":"走啦，點傾都冇用，并冇乜野係做完 然後佢地就唔會阻你行自己既人生路。"},{"pid":"cda9e8b7cd43cb34627e427253e70be261bd2dac","tid":2515162,"uid":284855,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T18:55:15.000Z","msg":"冇得處理，一定係後生走先，老人適應唔到轉變惟有留低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4733fb1e566b29588cd79feaa2a59ec8fd55e2a0","tid":2515162,"uid":13503,"like":39,"dislike":6,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T18:58:00.000Z","msg":"藍嘅人係叫唔醒幫佢哋申請定老人院到時候掟佢哋入去再賣埋間屋一了百了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9004692db3a19ee7ed024c246dbd512fb19f5c","tid":2515162,"uid":215044,"like":81,"dislike":5,"score":76,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T18:58:35.000Z","msg":"on9仲想帶兩個藍絲去加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍絲咁撚鍾意支那咪由佢地留係香港"},{"pid":"6b66aa1684f4be7f03266a17a299d314c3ef1716","tid":2515162,"uid":345459,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T19:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一於帶埋2藍2老去第2個世界吸下自由既空氣"},{"pid":"038ac8f4e77c6fa84547e3ad3c02fe569dec6b88","tid":2515162,"uid":131423,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T19:03:08.000Z","msg":"唔該你唔好帶藍絲黎加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37044cdb046ef8c75a0990318483b54bd2c7302b","tid":2515162,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T19:03:22.000Z","msg":"加拿大邊度"},{"pid":"05a55a5da84ab8e836faaf8b6e4ee778d0b9f803","tid":2515162,"uid":393495,"like":22,"dislike":4,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T20:25:48.000Z","msg":"父母為仔好就會支持你走，唔會喺度喊苦喊忽扮純情留你。你都係，扮下好喇，搵下邊間老人院招呼好啲嘅，睇下邊個老友/兄弟姊妹保證唔移民就交個父母畀佢閒時望下。<br />\n<br />\n諗下之後父母遺產稅點避好過，仲有幫佢兩個資產乾坤大挪移再入紙公屋，如果而家唔係住公居屋嘅話。"},{"pid":"331d80b7f3daeed659da727e6fdb17df3a32521d","tid":2515162,"uid":241811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T20:34:12.000Z","msg":"想問吓樓主，批咗要幾耐走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？"},{"pid":"c87ce6f86a80fdb78a3c5dee39790ccd9eabcf87","tid":2515162,"uid":82717,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T20:40:35.000Z","msg":"勤力啲打電話 用iPad FaceTime<br />\n努力賺錢 第時接埋佢地過黎囉 如果佢地可以適應到<br />\n理想歸理想 我走咗六年但屋企人仲未黎過"},{"pid":"6fd8c1ce6a46248ccc34258d00008ded612a8e97","tid":2515162,"uid":300578,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"038ac8f4e77c6fa84547e3ad3c02fe569dec6b88","tid":2515162,"uid":131423,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T19:03:08.000Z","msg":"唔該你唔好帶藍絲黎加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T20:41:29.000Z","msg":"冇撚錯<br />\n仆街啲都要講句，要團聚就留喺香港"},{"pid":"b42b51501d55836ebfb5bfb559a896867b341d64","tid":2515162,"uid":391437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"331d80b7f3daeed659da727e